com.exilant.exility.common

Class ObjectGetSetter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exilant.exility.common.ObjectGetSetter

  • public class ObjectGetSetter
extends Object
    Static utility Class to set/get field of/from an object we will not worry about any exception. We only promised that we will TRY :-)

      • getAll

        public static HashMap getAll(Object object,
                             boolean primitivesonly)
        Returns a HashMap of name/value pairs for all fields declared by the class or super classes Note: fields with 'private' modifiers are not picked up.
        Parameters:
        object - : object from which the fields are to be extracted
        primitivesonly - : Data types, int, Integer, float, Float, ..... and String are considered to be primitive If this field is set to true, fields of only these type are picked up. Else all fields are picked up.
        Returns:
        HashMap containing name/value pairs of all field values
